dvgrab (1.2.0deb-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream version 1.2. Removed outdated debian subdirectory from
    upstream tarball and renamed to 1.2.0deb. Closes: #186194
  * debian/copyright: Updated copyright entry. Mentioned removal of debian/
    from original tarball.
  * debian/control: Build depend on libquicktime, libjpeg and libdv. Bump
    standards version. Version debhelper build dependency. Mention new output
    formats in long description.
  * Makefile.am, Makefile.in: New header endian_types.h.
  * endian_types.h: Wrapper classes to transparently handle endianness
    conversions.
  * riff.h, riff.cc: Fix endianness issues in AVI output. Again.
  * avi.h: No padding in on-disk structures.
  * debian/rules: Bump debhelper compat level to 4. Support noopt build
    option. Proper invocation of configure.

